text:
Lord, we believe you founded our nation. Only you can preserve it.
Defeat the enemy's plans to destroy our Republic.
As you Delivered Moses & the children of Israel at the Red Sea, Please Deliver President Trump and us from this evil, fraudulent treachery.
In Jesus name, Amen.
Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV and @Isaiah53Lamb Romans 1:28-32 read it
Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV In Jesus Mighty Name, Amen
Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV In Jesus Name Amen

Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV Amen Amen 
thank you for your amazing prayers… 
We need God so much in our lives every single day and we especially need God now to save our republic
Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV Every day I pray for President Trump. I pray he goes away FOREVER

Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV Oh Lord, hear our prayers.

In Jesus name we pray.

Amen.
Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV In Jesus name we pray and ask you Amen

Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV and @prayerbloom “Part the waters for us as well, Lord, because our country needs broken hearts to come back to You. We ask You to build up the weak, to lift our heavy , so we may proclaim Your Victory  over this, too, Lord. We Praise You, we love You Jesus. Amen.”

Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV Precious Father, Just as you provided the inn for the birth of our Savior, You will provide a land Under God for your remnants. Thank you Heavenly Father. We Honor and Adore you.

Replying to @JohnTrumpFanKJV and @BibleBeltDarlin Amen & amen, O LORD our God.
As Lot asked the preincarnate Jesus, "What if only TEN faithful are found in Sodom/Gomorrah, will You destroy it?" The answer came, "For the sake of the ten, I will not destroy it," please have mercy on @POTUS & us, in Jesus Mighty Name, amen & amen

God bless you Concetta.
To God be the glory, great things he hath done.
